{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:07:21.898413+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "## Summary of the FastAPI Template Stack\n\n### Main Python Dependency\n**FastAPI** (with `all` extras) — the core web framework, served via **Uvicorn** (ASGI server).\n\n---\n\n### Service Stack (from `docker-compose.yml`)\n\n| Service | Image / Technology | Purpose |\n|---------|-------------------|---------|\n| **web** | Custom Docker build (FastAPI + Uvicorn) | Application server |\n| **postgres** | `postgres` (official image) | Primary relational database |\n| **redis** | `redis:alpine` | Caching / in-memory data store |\n\n---\n\n### Database Stack (PostgreSQL)\n\n- **SQLAlchemy** — ORM for model definitions and session management\n- **databases** (with `postgresql` extra) — async database query support for FastAPI\n- **psycopg2** — synchronous PostgreSQL adapter (used in the DB URL: `postgresql+psycopg2://...`)\n- **asyncpg** — asynchronous PostgreSQL driver\n- **sqlalchemy-utils** — helpers like `database_exists` / `create_database`\n- **Alembic** — database migrations (with `alembic.ini` and `alembic/` directory)\n\n---\n\n### Auth-Related Libraries\n\n- **python-jose** (with `cryptography` extra) — JWT token encoding/decoding (`jose.jwt`)\n- **passlib** (with `bcrypt` extra) — password hashing via `CryptContext(schemes=[\"bcrypt\"])`\n- **python-multipart** — required for OAuth2 form data parsing\n- **FastAPI's `OAuth2PasswordBearer`** — OpenAPI-compatible JWT authentication scheme\n\n---\n\n### Redis Support\n\n- **aioredis** — async Redis client library (Redis host/port configured in settings via `REDIS_HOST` / `REDIS_PORT` env vars)\n\n---\n\n### Additional\n\n- **pytest** — test framework\n- **Python version**: 3.9 (specified in `Pipfile`)", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 676, "prompt_tokens": 11053, "total_tokens": 11729, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 230, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 10880}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 10880, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 173}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-pro", "system_fingerprint": "fp_9954b31ca7_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "4bd61c51-c4f1-4d88-aa1d-4149c34094c2", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3b2-54df-7681-9933-0325e12131a7-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 11053, "output_tokens": 676, "total_tokens": 11729, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 10880}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 230}}}}]}}}
